Our Team




Some firms pretend to do everything well. We stick to our strengths.
The professional backgrounds of HWG’s attorneys and advisors reflect the diversity of the firm’s practice. Most of our attorneys have served in government – many in high-ranking offices – whether at the FCC, in the Department of Justice, the Department of Energy, the White House, or on Capitol Hill. Some of us have also clerked for judges of the federal courts, including two who served as U.S. Supreme Court clerks. Coupled with our broad experience in private practice, these varied backgrounds enable us to provide an extraordinary range of services for a firm of our size.







